{"tid":227602,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"出街溝女一定要請佢食手作雪糕","createTime":"2017-05-03T09:58:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-03T13:23:36.000Z","uid":29320,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0f41a80756b81006ae5078095a16e812ea5c82c8","tid":227602,"uid":29320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T09:58:21.000Z","msg":"第一步你要約到條女出街。<br />\n<br />\n跟住呢你就帶條女去手作之店食雪糕<br />\n<br />\n點解要去手作之店呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平囉抵食囉多細菌囉，最重要係手作之店啲員工全部都係女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去到手作之店呢唔使諗直接買＄12一球雪糕(相信好多巴打都負擔到)<br />\n<br />\n你求其買一隻味道比個女仔食，咁樣顯得你好有主見做人好有目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住你響褲袋掏出你嘅＄12，大大力拍響張收銀枱度。然後同個雪糕妹講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   唔該要一球雪糕！唔使找！<br />\n呢一刻你響個女仔同埋雪糕妹心目中形象係 型！瀟灑！大方！(如果最後溝唔到條女可以返去溝個雪糕妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n咁你淨係買咗一球雪糕，然後你就可以同條女玩下互餵遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ps 巴打唔好食咁多啖真係好多細菌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後呢你條女食完咁撚多細菌嘅雪糕。 返到屋企佢一定會搞肚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後巴打你就可以自然去關心佢啦。上去屋企比碗粥佢食。。跟住唔使我教喇<br />\n<br />\n食一個雪糕咁就可以幫你大大提升你係條女嘅心目中形象。仲有機會bye one get one Q <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n請女食手作雪糕真係無得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"733b35c631c84b516f56e1f1cd54816acbfc2e33","tid":227602,"uid":100442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T10:11:17.000Z","msg":"樓主幾時比狗屌？"},{"pid":"c571c6e634a2348bd42d8ce152aef8949e16cf6a","tid":227602,"uid":70249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T10:18:30.000Z","msg":"食咁多次手作都無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c888112b86b4bd3f0ee87e89fb3a9b2cf553b34","tid":227602,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T10:20:08.000Z","msg":"零分重作"},{"pid":"c52d52cae17ea9e8654273edcee33d1a15d1086e","tid":227602,"uid":62969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T10:32:41.000Z","msg":"零分"},{"pid":"4abdf1afbcf87f7e1324623c81eeae5c82c86d1d","tid":227602,"uid":51039,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T10:37:00.000Z","msg":"肚痛點會俾你屌呀<br />\nfail<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"094f52976c1d283211eb335a805defdaad77661e","tid":227602,"uid":29202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T10:42:42.000Z","msg":"潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0f4ef2986546ae081cf62600a40d736f5298cb9","tid":227602,"uid":38274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T10:49:16.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪睇左之前達哥讀果篇潮文 識食雪糕一定係食手作雪糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9a2a00d2ffce1da69f0ba96244e3f41ee492961","tid":227602,"uid":29320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T10:57:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食咁多次手作都無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我次次食親都肚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過為咗雪榚妹我都照食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d32a52e89d9e3bfea89cccd3d0f606fbe2f8da19","tid":227602,"uid":29320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T10:58:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主係咪睇